{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-posts-asciidoc-page-attributes-slug-tsx","path":"/posts/linux-grub2/","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"4568ec6d-b91d-5a8f-801b-a3047f89baab","html":"<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_更新_grub_cfg\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_更新_grub_cfg\"></a>更新 grub.cfg</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>fedora 35</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">sudo grub2-mkconfig -o /etc/grub2.cfg\nsudo grub2-mkconfig -o /etc/grub2-efi.cfg</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>fedora 34+ 不要执行\n<code>grub2-mkconfig -o /boot/efi/EFI/fedora/grub.cfg</code>，该文件会使用\n<code>/boot/grub2/grub.cfg</code>：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">$ cat /boot/efi/EFI/fedora/grub.cfg\nsearch --no-floppy --fs-uuid --set=dev 70ae6847-1c61-49f9-a09a-d5c65d04de28\nset prefix=($dev)/boot/grub2\n\nexport $prefix\nconfigfile $prefix/grub.cfg</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>参考：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/GRUB_2#Updating_the_GRUB_configuration_file\" class=\"bare\">https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/GRUB_2#Updating_the_GRUB_configuration_file</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"Linux GRUB2"},"pageAttributes":{"slug":"linux-grub2","category":"linux"},"revision":{"date":"2021-12-01","number":"1.0"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"4568ec6d-b91d-5a8f-801b-a3047f89baab","pageAttributes__slug":"linux-grub2","__params":{"pageAttributes__slug":"linux-grub2"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3143286284"],"slicesMap":{}}